Package: fcwtr
Type: Package
Title: Fast Continuous Wavelet Transform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lukas", "Schneiderbauer", email = "lukas.schneiderbauer@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Lukas", "Arts", role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Lukas Schneiderbauer <lukas.schneiderbauer@gmail.com>
Description: Utilizes and bundles the fCWT C++ library by Lukas Arts to make it
    available via an R package (using Rcpp).
    In addition, the package includes some helpers and sugar to make it easier
    working with the data as data frame. It automatically establishes a link to
    physical units and provides a plotting function.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    tidyr (>= 1.1.4),
    dplyr (>= 1.0.10),
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
Suggests:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.5),
    viridis (>= 0.6.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
